246998.視点固定と 家具・庭具リストの 説明です。\n<br>\n家具や庭具を 配置する:
This is an explanation of viewpoint fixation and the furniture/garden furniture list, which is used to place furniture and garden
furniture.You can place furniture and garden furniture from the furniture/garden furniture list in the items to create a series of placements.
The furniture and garden furniture to be moved in and out of the garden storage and furniture storage can be set in the door menu of each
house. If you have not yet built a house anywhere, please check the sign and build a house.

246999.同じ機能をもつ庭具の数が マイタウン内の敷地と\n庭具倉庫内を合わせて 上限まで:
I cannot store <%sL_ITEM> because the number of garden furniture with the same function is limited to the number of sites in My Town and
in the garden storage.

247699.『庭具倉庫』の 説明です。\n<br>\nマイタウンでは つかうものからの\n庭:
In My Town, in addition to placing garden furniture from items, you can share and place garden furniture owned by other people. By
inserting garden furniture from items into "garden storage" in the door menu, you can place garden furniture shared with the owner
or other authorized persons. The "garden storage" is the space for managing the garden furniture in My Town. The garden furniture in
the list with the word "warehouse" is shared by the owner or other authorized persons who have placed it in the "garden storage". The
number of garden furniture in My Town is limited to the number of garden furniture in the "garden storage" and the number of garden
furniture currently placed in the "garden storage". The number of garden furniture available in My Town is 150, including the
"garden storage" and the currently placed garden furniture. You can also try to put garden furniture in items by selecting
"directly touch and put away". Please try it out and create an attractive My Town by using "garden storage" and arranging various garden
furniture.
